Title: Arch Linux - News: Valkey to replace Redis in the [extra] Repository
Description: Valkey, a high-performance key/value datastore, will be replacing redis in the [extra] repository. This change is due to Redis modifying its license from BSD-3-Clause to RSALv2 and SSPLv1 on March 20th, 2024.
